Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:45.89,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,An endless road ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:50.35,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Two extremities of love and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:55.06,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Inner demons shrouding the heart—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:58.47,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,they wallow in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:02.27,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where is my old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:06.35,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,He is lingering in the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:13.18,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,convinced that he hasn't veered too far off course, in this world of fleeting destinies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:19.81,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why do you pine? Why do you yearn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:24.39,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Nowhere to turn—it's a path of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:28.60,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,The way of life is vicious, we keep going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:30.93,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Hard to discern the truths from the lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.02,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,tell the evil from the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:36.52,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,In front of my eyes, a gnarled mess of mountains and waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:41.18,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why do you tread a path this treacherous?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:45.43,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Embroiled in sinister schemes, in trepidation as the tables turn and turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:47.89,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,I bid you adieu—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:51.60,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,shall we never meet again!
