Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:13.52,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Time has
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:17.60,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,drowned out even the claps of thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.43,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,They scatter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:23.39,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,the cut-up fragments of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:29.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,I can only fumble around, trying to piece them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:33.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why must I climb mountains and peaks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.06,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,to collect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:39.06,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,the shadows of hanging onto someone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:42.10,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,however late I always seem to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:47.89,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Those places where I once walked,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:52.10,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,what did they
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:56.06,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,look like originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:03.72,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Trying to trace those footsteps behind me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:07.89,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,I have forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:13.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,as the path I came from was too far and too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:19.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will be the end of my journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:23.31,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.47,0:24:27.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.02,0:24:30.35,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be...
