Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say I'm a little shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a hungry ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Try eating only celery and preserved carrots for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm here, I'm gonna eat whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we go take a look elsewhere as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows if you still remember how you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what you'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if we can't find the pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I left a mark there back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In forests and mountains that deep,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,what mark wouldn't wear off after 3 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That mark of mine could last for 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,let alone 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go wrong with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sketch the entire route even with my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be absolutely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to Ah-da to trade local goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,where are you two planning to do your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to dig up local goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here to promote local specialties?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell them somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:48.77,annotation,,0,0,0,,Grave robbing jargon: "Virgins" - people not of the trade; "going up into the hills" - to rob a grave
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just two virgins who aren't going up into the hills.
Comment: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wuzi: from the novel - "Just two innocent virgins who aren't going up into the hills."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm full.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy just now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,used a type of jargon when he spoke to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Trading local goods" is jargon for grave-robbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to sound us out, to see if we're also in the same line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They reek of mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably here to clean out some graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I reckon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,they became suspicious after hearing our chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we really caught their attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be quite troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, no need to leave though?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ways to hold them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What can they do to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too naive, Lao Wu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say you're not an amateur ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The underworld is complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,watch and learn from your brother—me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll set off tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter Mount Changyang from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,ride for three hours, then transfer to Jialing River.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're quick, the journey will take less than a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we reach Mount Taibai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll travel along the scenic route.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see what a pro I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,E-E-Earthquake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You two must be from out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet someone's bombing the tombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,With that blast just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,someone must've knocked over the explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have the guts to do such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a local specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A gang of them got arrested just a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kids here for sightseeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're planning to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're planning to visit Mount Taibai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The tour group won't take you any deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There are all sorts of twists and turns in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can easily get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an accident just a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Some art school kids went in the mountains to sketch,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and they never came back afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,People know my name around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to be your guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:33.31,TOP-TEXT,,0,0,0,,[PRICE LIST]\NCharter Car - 600 yuan/day, Homestay - 300 yuan/day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mount Serpent Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest point
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is more than a kilometer above sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to visit a proper ethnic village,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to climb the mountain on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On that mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,countless people have lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we find a place to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you keep boasting when you're this weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you even keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,(Mount Taibai Scenic Area)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,were they the ones we met last night in the night market?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:41.60,TOP-TEXT,,0,0,0,,[It is honorable to prevent fires; it is shameful to commit arson]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me they heard what we said over dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided to follow us, looking for a chance to stop us midway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all that gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They came prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If they see us here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they might just get suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and see us as a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we fall back first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll enter the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Tai,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,give us an estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer until we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we make it past Mount Serpent Head,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,where there are trails, we need to walk for two more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where there are no trails, I can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't take it, you'd better leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This deal can feed us for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The hard work will pay off eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lee is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as we close this deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we can all retire early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get ahead of yourselves just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know for certain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if the tomb is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better pray the information is true, Mr. Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lao Tai,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you always worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've worked together for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When have I ever failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There will definitely be no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, we'll leave the country together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have plenty of land to play with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Wu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we following them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,T-These are all dangerous outlaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll lead us out of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That tour guide mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,most trails are sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never make it without a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of trying our luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we might as well get a free ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Wu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I think we should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm gonna die if we keep walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still a long way from the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they'll also be tired soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After we follow them to their camp site,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll stop for a rest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,follow them forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows if they're leaving the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What if t-they follow their guide
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and just go d-deeper into the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so haughty when nothing's sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We did work together for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never knew where you got your information from.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never regret visiting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,where we're going this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also the last time we're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not too much of a taboo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,tell us brothers about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach us a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been guessing all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a special technique of some sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You always find ancient tombs easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't tell others about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you guys really want to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you in on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not exactly a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got to do with my ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the late Qing dynasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,my family were once landowners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We were relocating our ancestral graves
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,one year, when some workers accidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,knocked over a coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The bones inside
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,spilled all over the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As we were picking up the remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,my grandfather discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that while everything in the coffin had rotted away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,there was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a cloth with symbols drawn all over it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that still remained intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Wu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as risky as it gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just gonna go confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if they plan on leaving the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear a thing I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are dangerous outlaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather found it strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so he gave the cloth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to a relative who did business in antiques.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,they realized there was something more to that cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The words on the fabric
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.64,annotation,,0,0,0,,* 哑文 (Yawen): a language used by deaf or mute people (in folklore).
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,were written in {\i1}Yawen{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know what that cloth was used for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a few things about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Legend has it that during the Northern Wei dynasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an army of deaf-mutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This was probably what they used to pass around secret information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The words on it were written in Yawen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from our advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would such a thing be in the coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather was curious, so he went back and checked our ancestral record.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, he found a certain event written in the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was during the Northern Wei dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the land was war-stricken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,God knows how many wars broke out every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That year, my ancestor wasn't even six years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Riots erupted near the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone managed to flee
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,except for their family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside, people fought and killed like madmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Things didn't quiet down until the third day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My ancestor was scared out of his wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He sneakily climbed out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,only to find bodies strewn everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't tell the soldiers from the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a wounded deaf-mute soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My ancestor took pity on him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave him some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But the deaf-mute soldier's injuries were truly too grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He died shortly after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Before his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he took out a piece of linen inscribed with words
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave it to my ancestor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,my ancestor had no idea what was written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, that piece of cloth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,was used as fabric for a cotton coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The family rose and fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and when he passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that cotton coat was buried along with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was written on that piece of cloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the creation of this Northern Wei army
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was inspired by Cao Cao's grave-robbing troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On the surface, they were the emperor's guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but in secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they also robbed graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As they were deaf-mutes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and used Yawen, a language only they understood,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the ancient tombs they robbed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,were known by only them and the emperor himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Their traces
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,had always been mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lee,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,don't tell me, that piece of linen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is the River Wood Scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With you around, Mr. Advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even keep you guys guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That really is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Different lives, different fates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lees are destined for riches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what exactly is the River Wood Scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that whenever the deaf-mute army found an ancient tomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't excavate it straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They would first make a record,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,level the ground on horseback, then pour molten lead over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When needed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd trace back to the tombs using the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What recorded the locations of the tombs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was called the River Wood Scroll,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a homophone for "where tombs lie."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you being a little too secretive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With such a treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you should've told us more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't intending to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That white cloth my ancestor left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,records the positions of 24 ancient tombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The one we're going to this time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most mysterious of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,According to what was written,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the treasures in this tomb
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot be enjoyed by any common man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This tomb is the king of all treasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,better than even the Mausoleum of the First Qin Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can trust me on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You think what Lee's saying is real?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can there really be a grave better than the Mausoleum of the First Qin Emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But he sounds so confident about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be after something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll leave the mountain tomorrow for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep following them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:37.47,TOP-TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,126)}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU JERK!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's lighting a fire over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Mountain Patrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be trouble if the Mountain Patrol catches us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Tai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't going to follow them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but you insisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We almost died there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to run the moment they found us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reaction was way too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You only called me after scooting off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You're heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My fault, my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and find the tracks they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still not giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't find our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be trapped in the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Wu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,think again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, we gotta give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- ... tourists!     -Tourists?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at how shady you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're either grave-robbers or poachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to fool me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a long way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't just run your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With which eye did you see us dig graves or poach?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's 100 yuan, I need some directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Any more nonsense, and I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come across too many folks like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you'll scare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the knife away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We just ran into the Mountain Patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They told us to look out for strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume you're backpackers headed for our village?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to turn left and go around this hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be a waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the water and keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll arrive at our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How... How long would we still have to walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to spend the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you come along with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're returning to the village too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:21:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for leading the way then, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those behind, keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Wu,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,just ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a small hut for herb gatherers.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,TEXT,0,0,0,,TEXT
